text: Mohammad Keramat Ali is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Patuakhali-1. ==Career== Ali was elected to parliament from Patuakhali-1 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mohammad Keramat Ali
